---
const milestones = [
  {
    version: 'v0.1.0',
    title: 'The first release',
    body: 'Opus orchestrator handled everything. Worked, but the orchestrator was slow on misuse cases — it would try to produce a phased plan even for analysis questions, stalling for tens of seconds.',
    lesson: 'A heavyweight orchestrator is wrong for routing. The right tool is a fast classifier, not a deep planner.',
  },
  {
    version: 'v0.1.2',
    title: 'Sonnet front-door agent',
    body: 'Added a Sonnet agent in front of the Opus orchestrator to classify and refuse misuse fast. Still slow because forking ANY agent adds latency — process spawn, context transfer, model warm-up. The fix didn\'t fix.',
    lesson: 'Forking is the latency cost, not model size. Stacking specialist agents only makes it worse.',
  },
  {
    version: 'v0.1.3',
    title: 'Non-forked smart skill',
    body: 'Removed the forking front-door entirely. /yukti:smart is now a non-forked skill — its routing logic runs in your existing Claude Code session, no extra fork. Analysis questions answered at plain-chat speed. Code changes still fork to the specialist pipeline (justified — that\'s where the savings live).',
    lesson: 'For routing, the fastest fork is no fork.',
  },
];
---

<section class="story" id="story" aria-labelledby="story-h">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow" data-reveal>The story</span>
    <h2 id="story-h" data-reveal>Three architecture iterations in one day.</h2>
    <p class="story-lead" data-reveal>
      Real users hit slowness on a v0.1.0 prompt the same evening of release. Each iteration was a response to a specific complaint, with the receipt in the commit log. Honest changelogs, no marketing spin.
    </p>

    <ol class="timeline" data-reveal>
      {milestones.map((m, i) => (
        <li class="milestone" style={`--delay: ${i * 100}ms`}>
          <div class="milestone-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="32" height="32" fill="none">
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="14" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="2" fill="var(--paper)" />
              <circle cx="16" cy="16" r="6" fill="var(--accent)" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <header>
              <span class="milestone-version">{m.version}</span>
              <h3>{m.title}</h3>
            </header>
            <p>{m.body}</p>
            <p class="lesson">
              <span class="lesson-label">Lesson:</span> {m.lesson}
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>

    <p class="story-foot" data-reveal>
      Read the full commit log at <a href="https://github.com/akii09/yukti/commits/main" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/akii09/yukti/commits</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story { background: var(--paper); }

  .story-lead {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 16px;
    top: 16px;
    bottom: 16px;
    width: 2px;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--grey-soft) 50%, transparent 50%);
    background-size: 2px 8px;
  }

  .milestone {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 60px;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .milestone:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

  .milestone-mark {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--paper);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .milestone-content header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .milestone-version {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-ink);
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    padding: 0.18rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .milestone-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .milestone-content p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .lesson {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 0.85rem;
    background: var(--paper-2);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .lesson-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--accent-ink);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-right: 0.3rem;
  }

  .story-foot { color: var(--grey); font-size: 0.92rem; }
</style>
